"Draconic blood gives a high resistant against fire, but vulerable against the"
" cold. Rashy with that trait grow tougher with age and gain additional "
"hitpoints. Because of their heat resistance, thay tend to fight and move "
"better in the desert.\n"
"\n"
"+20% fire resistance, -10% cold resistance, +2HP per level, better sand "
"movement and +10% sand defense"
msgstr ""

