msgid "race^Angels"
msgstr ""

#. [race], id=AE_RHY_angel
#: .\units\RE_units\races.cfg:8
msgid ""
"To gain more support from the religios smallfolk, the Luz Highpriest had "
"given order to create holy beings. The Luz captured Harpies and bred them to "
"create a new humanoid species with white wings. Those creatures are raised "
"and manipulated from their birth to follow the orders of the Inquisition "
"without question. The thruth of the Angels origin is hidden from anyone other"
" than the highest ranking Inquisitors and Priests.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"Angels have hollow bones and a very fragile body to be light enough to fly. "
"Though they are not holy by nature, Angles are constantly influenced by the "
"magic of the Inquisitors during their youth which results in a higher "
"resistance against arcanary."
msgstr ""

#. [race], id=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\races.cfg:17
msgid "race^Animal"
msgstr ""

#. [race], id=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\races.cfg:18
