#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Vortex, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\m3-MageVortex.cfg:4
msgid "Rashy Vortexmage"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Vortex, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\m3-MageVortex.cfg:19
msgid ""
"It is not sure where the Vortexmages draw their power from, but the result is"
" overwhelming. They can cast storms of pure electrical energy to turn anyone "
"into dust."
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\m3-MageVortex.cfg:53
msgid "female^Rashy Vortexmage"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Researcher, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb1-MageResearcher.cfg:4
msgid "Rashy Researcher"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Researcher, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb1-MageResearcher.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Rashy Researchers are the driving force of all discoveries made by the "
"Trarashy. Their focus often lies on mundane thing, like cooking, smithing and"
" growing crops, but most researchers are studying the higher mysteries as "
"well. Researchers know the essence of Magic itself and can use it to conjure "
"almost everything, granted that they have learned how to do this."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb1-MageResearcher.cfg:27
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-Healer.cfg:32
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-MageDimension.cfg:32
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:37
