msgid "impulse"
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb1-MageResearcher.cfg:119
msgid "female^Rashy Researcher"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Healer, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-Healer.cfg:4
msgid "Rashy Alchemist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Healer, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-Healer.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Some Mages can use their arcane knowledge to manipulate the body. As this "
"knowledge can be highly dangerous, if used for evil, the usage is highly "
"restricted and only allowed in order to heal people. Experiments on oneself "
"is forbidden as it can lead to horrible mishaps."
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-Healer.cfg:124
msgid "female^Rashy Alchemist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Dimension, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-MageDimension.cfg:4
msgid "Rashy Dimensionmage"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Dimension, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-MageDimension.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The most interesting discovery made by Researchers is the control of the very"
" fabric of the universe. This kind of magic is difficult to master, but "
"Dimensionmages can use enough of it to distort space, allowing them to warp "
"between many places and to tear others apart. Dimension Mages never use their"
" full strengh, as it is exhausting and can rip a permanent hole in space, if "
"they are not careful."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-MageDimension.cfg:44
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:49
msgid "space disruption"
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb2-MageDimension.cfg:121
msgid "female^Rashy Dimensionmage"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Time, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:4
msgid "Rashy Chronomancer"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Time, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:19
msgid ""
"With their ability to control time and space Chronomancers can dodge physical"
" attacks easier, but it makes them vulnerable against manipulation of magic. "
"Aside from space distortion they posess the ability to slow time for a short "
"while."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:61
msgid "time disruption"
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\mb3-MageTime.cfg:146
msgid "female^Rashy Timemage"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Outrider, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\Outrider.cfg:4
msgid "Trarashy Avantgarde"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Avatar, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\Rashky_Avatar.cfg:4
msgid "Rashky Avatar"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_tr_Avatar, race=AE_RHY_rashy
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\Rashky_Avatar.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Since the Rashkys have left this world, only few can summon their power. On "
"the toll of their own life high mages can turn into an avatar. These avatars "
"can call upon a tremendous amount of cosmical energy, but it shortens their "
"lifespan with every use."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\Rashky_Avatar.cfg:47
msgid "universial energy"
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\RE_units\trarashy\Rashky_Avatar.cfg:133
