#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Archer, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\a1-Archer.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Archer"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Archer, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\a1-Archer.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Raised in a civilisation of warriors and hunters, Amazon archer show "
"dexterity similar to elves when it comes to bows. Their light, foxlike body "
"is adapted perfectly to the thick rainforest of their homeland."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Marksman, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\a2-Marksman.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Marksman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Sharpshooter, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\a3-Sharpshooter.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Sharpshooter"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Hunter, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f1-Amazon_hunter.cfg:4
msgid "Amazon Huntress"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Hunter, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f1-Amazon_hunter.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Due to their speed and dexterity the amazon hunters belong to the deadliest "
"predators in the world. Their archery is usually enough for hunting small "
"wildlife, but the rather short spears even prove useful during war."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Guard, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f2-Amazon_guard.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Guard"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Guard, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f2-Amazon_guard.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Amazon guards have longer spears and are tasked with the protection of "
"villages an leaders."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Stalker, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f2-Amazon_stalker.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Stalker"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Stalker, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f2-Amazon_stalker.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Amazon stalkers are unmatched in speed by any other infantry. While they "
"usually run on two feet, they sometimes sprint on all fours or climb and jump"
" on the trees in the Amazon rainforest. Thanks to their green clothing and "
"silent movement, they can easily hide in the thick bushes and forests of "
"their homeland. They use poison darts to weaken their prey and then strike "
"their daggers into the back, when the victim tries to flee."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f2-Amazon_stalker.cfg:57
msgid "poison dart"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Queen, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f3-Amazon_queen.cfg:4
msgid "Amazon Matriarch"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Queen, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f3-Amazon_queen.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Experienced in combat and war, the Matriarchs are accepted leaders of the "
"amazon tribes. Smaller tribes have a single leader, while bigger tribes rely "
"on the wisdom of a small council."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Templeguard, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f3-Amazon_templeguard.cfg:5
msgid "female^Amazon Templeguard"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Templeguard, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\f3-Amazon_templeguard.cfg:19
msgid ""
"As expert warriors with bow and spear, the Templeguards defend the fragile "
"priests."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Godess, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\Godess.cfg:4
msgid "Amazon Godess"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Godess, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\Godess.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Cerya the living godess of hunt is leader of the largest amazon tribe. Her "
"numerous talents makes her adored by her people and feared by her foes."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Shaman, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h1-Shaman.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Shaman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Shaman, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h1-Shaman.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Amazon Shamans often work as acolytes in the temples or seek solitude outside"
" the towns. They perform bloodmagic to heal themself or others with it."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h1-Shaman.cfg:34
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Priest.cfg:28
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Highpriest.cfg:34
msgid "shiv"
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h1-Shaman.cfg:42
msgid "breeze"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Priest, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Priest.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Priest"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Priest, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Priest.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The Priest are responsible for the rituals and ceremonial offerings to please"
" the Amazon goddess."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Priest.cfg:36
msgid "wind"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Sorceress, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Witch.cfg:4
msgid "Amazon Witch"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Sorceress, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Witch.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Witches focus more on offensive windmagic than bloody rituals. They can "
"create poweful storms, even at short range, to blast enemies away."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Witch.cfg:25
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Elderwitch.cfg:31
msgid "stormfist"
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h2-Shaman_Witch.cfg:37
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Highpriest.cfg:42
msgid "storm"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Witch, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Elderwitch.cfg:4
msgid "Amazon Elder Witch"
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Elderwitch.cfg:43
msgid "tornado"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Highpriest, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\h3-Shaman_Highpriest.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Highpriest"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Scout, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\s1-Jaguar_scout.cfg:4
msgid "female^Jaguar Scout"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Scout, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\s1-Jaguar_scout.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Jaguars are ferocious beasts that stalk the jungle. Any sane person would try"
" to avoid them at all costs, but the Amazone vixen managed to capture young "
"cubs and raise them. After many generations they became rideable beasts."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Rider, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\s2-Jaguar_rider.cfg:4
msgid "female^Jaguar Rider"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Knight, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\s3-Jaguar_hunter.cfg:4
msgid "Jaguar Huntress"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Anakonda, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_anakonda.cfg:4
msgid "Anaconda"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Anakonda, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_anakonda.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The largest anacondas in the jungle can grow over 9 meter and posess "
"overpowering strength. Once they wrap around their victims there is no escape"
" from the snake's grip. Their size and dislocateable jaw allows them to "
"swallow their prey whole."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_anakonda.cfg:43
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_viper.cfg:41
msgid "strangle"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Swamp, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_swamp.cfg:4
msgid "Swamp Snake"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Swamp, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_swamp.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The smaller snakes have acquired a venomous bite through evolution. Smaller "
"prey drops dead in mere minutes. Bitten persons experience an immense pain "
"from the venom and are severely weakened until cured."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Viper, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_viper.cfg:4
msgid "Viper"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Snake_Viper, race=AE_RHY_animal
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\snake_viper.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Vipers can grow a few meters long and are able to strangle people to their "
"death. Once their prey is weakened form their venomous fangs they suffocate "
"them by wrapping around them."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Clubber, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w1-Clubber.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Clubber"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Clubber, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w1-Clubber.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Not all Vixen-Amazones are lightfooted. Those who are not try to specialize "
"on heavier equipment. They build clubs from wooden branches and sharp stones "
"and carry large leathern shields. To rob the enemy of the speed advantage, "
"the Amazon clubbers tie them up with precisely thrown bolas."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Warrior, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w2-Warrior.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Warrior"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Warrior, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w2-Warrior.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Amazones who made fun of the clumsiness of clubbers still shiver at the "
"thought of fighting against a battlehardend warrior. While they may not be as"
" fast or as agile as the hunters, their endurance and strength is not matched"
" by any other of their kin."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Smasher, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w3-Smasher.cfg:4
msgid "female^Amazon Smasher"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_rhy_vx_Smasher, race=AE_RHY_vixen, gender=female
#: .\units\RE_units\vixens\w3-Smasher.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Legendary Warriors among the Amazones can aquire the rank of smashers. They "
"wear the hide of killed animals to show of their might and intimidate anyone,"
" who dares to oppose them. Especially experienced Smashers can learn to throw"
" their bolas even faster."
msgstr ""
